data.title: SENNHEISER G4ME ZERO 2 x 3.5 mm Connector Circumaural Gaming Headset Overview
data.description: Hear every nuance with the Sennheiser G4ME ZERO headset. The G4ME ZERO is the first-ever gaming headset to feature multiple layers of fitted ear padding. This design delivers the ultimate in sound leakage blocking from inside and out, so you can hear every detail of your game while not disturbing others in the proximity. German-engineered speaker technology and a top-notch noise-cancelling microphone deliver outstanding hi-fi performance that lets you focus on the game, not your headset. The microphone can be muted by simply rotating the boom out of the way. Along with the volume control integrated on the right ear cup, you can quickly crank up or down without missing any action.

data.title: Enermax AeroOdio 17" Speaker Notebook Cooling Pad w/ 220mm Fan Overview
data.description: The AeroOdio CP006 Cooling Pad is designed to keep your notebook running cool and sounding great. This cooling pad features a 22cm powerful fan with manual speed control, as well as a dock set with two external speakers. The integrated DreamBass sound chip equipped with the speakers provides premium full-surround sound with deep bass and crystal-clear highs. Moreover, the AeroOdio CP006 also features smart cable management system to assort various types of cables for your laptop and peripherals.

data.title: Enermax TwisterOdio CP008 16" Aluminum Surface Speaker Notebook Cooling Pad Overview
data.description: The TWISTERODIO 16 CP008 Notebook Cooler not only lowers your notebook's temperature, but also provides fantastic stereo sound. The two built-in satellite drivers are powered by the DreamBass sound chip for a full-surround sound experience with deep bass. Now, your notebook cooler can do more. It is compatible with notebooks of up to 16 inches in size.

data.title: Enermax Aeolus Vegas 17" Aluminum Gaming Notebook Cooling Pad Overview
data.description: The Aeolus Vegas CP007 Laptop Cooler cools a notebook up to 17 inches, with an 18cm four-color (blue, red, green and white) LED fan, and a cooling area of up to 420mm. Four lighting modes, aluminum fins, steel mesh, and stylish rubber edges deliver eye-appealing cool effects.

data.title: TRENDnet TEW-800MB AC1200 Dual Band Wireless Media Bridge Overview
data.description: The AC1200 Dual Band Wireless Media Bridge, model TEW-800MB, connects up to four devices around your entertainment center to a revolutionary Wireless AC network. Connect a network-enabled TV, media player, gaming console, and receiver to the Gigabit ports. Wireless AC easily handles multiple HD streams simultaneously.

data.title: WD Black² Dual Drive 2.5" 120 GB SSD + 1 TB HDD Kit  Tutorial
data.description: WD has redefined the PC with the next big thing in ultra-fast performance storage. Introducing WD Black², the world's first 2.5-inch dual drive storage solution. The WD Black² dual drive is a completely new approach in a compromised solid-state and hybrid storage market. Finally you can have the speed of an SSD that you want and the capacity of a hard drive that you need in your notebook or all-in-one PC.

data.title: Azio G8 GM8200 USB Wired Laser 8200 dpi Gaming Class Mouse Overview
data.description: Designed for the gaming enthusiast, the Azio G8 is an awesome hybrid between a high-grade functional mouse and a programmable gaming mouse. Users can easily switch between 800 to 8200dpi on-the-fly. With its Macro-able nine buttons in five profiles, the G8 strives for the perfect blend between form and function.
